subproject.description: The project aims to deepen the understanding of the role of paid and unpaid care in the development process and for gender equality in particular, with a view to providing insights to the design of economic and social policies.  It is implemented by UNRISD.  Target countries include South Africa, India, Korea, Tanzania, Argentina, Nicaragua, and Japan.
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: CARE ECONOMY
